/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Block9@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Block9@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Block9@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a>公布了 Block9 2024 年演出阵容，并确认户外舞蹈区 Genosys 回归。查找下面的所有详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-set-times-stage-splits-3749871"><b>格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 2024：查看迄今为止的完整阵容和舞台划分</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>传奇的 Worthy Farm 活动将于下个月回归， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shania-twain">Shania Twain</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lcd-soundsystem">LCD Soundsystem</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a>等乐队都会成为头条新闻。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-revealed-who-playing-poster-3600775">第一波演出已于三月份得到确认</a>，从那时起，组织者就开始为音乐节的许多区域和舞台分别投放海报，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-english-teacher-sprints-bob-vylan-and-lottery-winners-among-acts-for-left-field-line-up-3752348">Left Field</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-announce-stacked-line-up-for-woodsies-area-3752059">Woodsies</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/faithless-fatboy-slim-camelphat-groove-armada-lead-glastonbury-2024-glade-area-line-up-3749471">The Glade</a> 、The <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-adds-more-names-to-line-up-acoustic-stage-3616963">Acoustic Stage</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-romy-kelly-lee-owens-shygirl-and-more-added-to-glastonbury-as-silver-hayes-line-up-revealed-3751900">Silver Hayes</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-announces-full-line-up-for-the-park-including-two-new-venues-3756495">The Park</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-festival-announces-2024-line-up-for-the-common-3753302">The常见的</a>。</p><p>现在，Glastonbury 已确认 2024 年 Block9 系列的详细信息；庆祝其首次推出 17 周年。</p><p>该地区于 2007 年兴起，通过音乐和创造力鼓励多样性、自由和协作，并已发展成为一个由志同道合的 DJ、制作人、表演艺术家、音乐家、技术人员、变装皇后和国王、活动家、舞者组成的社区。屠夫男孩、俱乐部孩子和狂欢者。</p><p>今年的演出还标志着期待已久的野兽派巨型户外舞蹈舞台 Genosys 以及传奇场地 The NYC Downlow、The Meat Rack 和 IICON 的回归。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">令人难以置信的<a href="https://twitter.com/block9official?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@block9official</a>为 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节带来了更多的业余活动，户外舞蹈舞台 Genosys 以及传奇场地 The NYC Downlow、The Meat Rack 和 IICON 的回归，提供了精彩的 DJ 和表演阵容。 <a href="https://t.co/xyFDUBQg1n">pic.twitter.com/xyFDUBQg1n</a></p><p> - 格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 (@glastonbury) <a href="https://twitter.com/glastonbury/status/1793914835299877354?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 5 月 24 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> <a href="/artists/confidence-man">Confidence Man</a>和<a href="/artists/bicep">Bicep</a>均已在最新更新中公布，还有<a href="/artists/honey-dijon">Honey Dijon</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eliza-rose">Eliza Rose</a> 、Sophie Lou、Luke Howard 和 A-Future。</p><p> Block9 的其他新公告包括 Niks、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/a-guy-called-gerald">A Guy Called Gerald</a> 、Deena、Husband、Wallace、Peach、Sugarbear、Scarlet O&#39;Malley 等。在上面的 Glaso 海报中可以找到完整的阵容。</p><p>今年的另一项新举措是，酷儿夜生活机构 NYC Downlow 将于周六（6 月 29 日）下午举办首届 Downlow Day Party。该活动将由纽约传奇人物 François K（Body &amp; Soul）主持。</p><p>时尚偶像兼活动家 Katharine Hamnett 也将与 Block9 联手，鼓励人们通过她的商标、充满力量的口号和立即可识别的图形风格投票。</p><p><a href="https://www.glastonburyfestivals.co.uk/areas/block9/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>了解有关 Block9 区域的更多信息。</p><p>预计未来几周将公布 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的更多地区公告。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-set-times-stage-splits-3749871">请访问此处查看迄今为止的完整阵容和舞台划分</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4fLcwiNTQ7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.